channel.title: Metasequoia serial key works for all versions!
channel.description:
[b]I found the metasequoia serial key for the full version and I thought why not share it (works on all versions):
ID:37D1Ca-4FE1
Password:WDZ4-iOoD-9TEw
For activating your copy of Metasequoia just run Metasequoia click on "Help" then click on "Registration", fill in the ID and password I gave you, hit OK and voilà, full acces to Meta. You can now edit RuneScape models with 3DS Max or any other 3D modeling software![/b]
